#FactCheck 
Claim: J&J #COVID19 #vaccine 100% effective 28 days post-jab at preventing COVID-19 hospitalizations (A) & deaths (B).

Rating: Misleading. A, post hoc analysis. B, no statistical significance. Neither deemed a shown benefit. Vox spreading #VaccineMisinformation https://t.co/FXWSK9uDoZ
